#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:265
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "We tried the \"AI does everything\" version. Agents that write emails, agents that decide who to contact, agents that personalise. It's expensive to keep stable and the output stinks of slop — recipients can tell. People are getting so much AI-written outreach now that even genuinely human emails are starting to read as suspicious."
msgstr "Vi prøvede \"AI klarer alt\"-versionen. Agenter, der skriver e-mails, agenter, der beslutter hvem der skal kontaktes, agenter, der personaliserer. Det er dyrt at holde stabilt, og outputtet stinker af AI-slop — modtagerne kan mærke det. Folk får så meget AI-skrevet outreach nu, at selv ægte menneskeskrevne e-mails begynder at virke mistænkelige."

